pytabcmd
========

**pytabcmd** is a simple python wrapper for tabcmd_. 
currently it works with tabcmd 9.2 in linux (and should work in windows too, but it's not tested).

.. _tabcmd: http://onlinehelp.tableau.com/current/server/en-us/tabcmd.htm
